citeinfo.origin: Dakota County GIS, Dakota County GIS, Staff
citeinfo.title: Road Centerlines, Dakota County, Minnesota

pubinfo.pubplace: 14955 Galaxie Ave, Apple Valley, Minnesota, 55124, US

descript.abstract: This layer contains lines showing all public (and many private) roads in Dakota County, Minnesota. The lines are generally collected from plats and aerial photography.
descript.purpose: A road centerline database that can be used for assigning addresses, geocoding, labeling and general cartographic dispaly.

theme.themekey: transportation, centerline, street, streets, road, roads, address, addressing

procstep.procdesc: Dakota County maintains road centerline data for internal purposes. General sources of information are plat centerlines and heads-up digitizing using aerial photography.
